Faculty and Staff 


Home // Faculty and Staff
Faculty and Staff
The Chronicle of Higher Education Great Colleges to Work For program evaluates universities on the basis of a dozen criteria such as teaching environment, facilities, compensation and benefits, and the faculty and staffs’ sense of respect and appreciation. Notre Dame has participated in the past two years, earning Honor Roll distinctions both years.

