Go “Beyond the Stage” with director Drew Fracher and members of the NDSF Professional Company cast and design team. Talk to actors, touch the costumes, and tour our star-spangled stage. The event is limited to two groups of 25. Identical tours will begin at 6 p.m. and 7 p.m. on Wednesday, Aug. 2, in the Patricia George Decio Mainstage Theatre, DeBatolo Performing Arts Center.






